Not long after your home visit,

71
00:04:09,350 --> 00:04:10,510
I saw Lu Zhengyang

72
00:04:10,510 --> 00:04:12,440
come out of No. 1899 Zhongbai Road.

73
00:04:14,860 --> 00:04:16,269
Now we can confirm

74
