292
00:17:10,349 --> 00:17:11,869
You did your best.

293
00:17:20,710 --> 00:17:22,440
I really didn't do well enough.

294
00:17:24,630 --> 00:17:26,470
So it's a burden for me

295
00:17:28,590 --> 00:17:29,790
