427
00:26:06,790 --> 00:26:07,640
And you

428
00:26:08,470 --> 00:26:10,610
were the seed

429
00:26:11,290 --> 00:26:13,420
he chose to protect with his life.

430
00:26:18,870 --> 00:26:19,860
Unfortunately,

431
00:26:20,890 --> 00:26:22,300
