465
00:28:17,190 --> 00:28:19,480
if you are Chen Rushan or Du Lengquan?

466
00:28:19,550 --> 00:28:21,430
I'm Chen Rushan!

467
00:28:25,430 --> 00:28:26,390
No, no, no.

468
00:28:26,540 --> 00:28:27,910
I'm not Chen Rushan.

469
00:28:29,110 --> 00:28:30,870
I'm Du Lengquan.

470
