517
00:33:03,060 --> 00:33:05,060
and a loser.

518
00:33:07,510 --> 00:33:08,580
I was wrong.

519
00:33:11,670 --> 00:33:13,160
I chose...

520
00:33:14,750 --> 00:33:16,510
